ygData.messageBody:
Cat's Eye Agate can be found in 2 maybe more place in the Nektulos Forest
area.

1) In guild. The person that sells the robes for Wizards also sells
Cat's Eye.

2) 4th Inn in East Commonlands (Near zone to West Commons)

Hope this helps anyone in need.

Shadiar J'Axx
23 Wizard
Karana

PS: Yes my secret Hunting grounds will come by Saturday it looks lie.
Should make 24 tonight. Averaging 4-6 hours per lvl here
